# Spotify Genre Classifier

This project predicts the genre of songs using Spotify audio features.

## Dataset
Spotify audio features dataset.

## Features Used
- danceability
- energy
- loudness
- speechiness
- acousticness
- instrumentalness
- liveness
- valence
- tempo

## Model
Random Forest Classifier

## Accuracy
0.22346491228070176 or 22.346%
## Tools
Python, Pandas, Scikit-Learn, Google Colab
